                      <p>Shapes the dashboard system and mobile-first patterns.</p>
                      <ul class="team__socials">
                        <li>
                          <a href="https://twitter.com/saaskit" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"><i class="fa-brands fa-twitter"></i></a>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                          <a href="https://dribbble.com" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"><i class="fa-brands fa-dribbble"></i></a>
                        </li>
                      </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-12 col-sm-6 team__item">
